column5: Myself, woke up at 3 am, gonna head back to bed soon, as I do not have to work today.  You going fishin for steel today Cliff, or just getting up for work?
Guess it depends which Cliff LOL, I (Big Cliff) have been up and working for about two hours now and just decided to take a break. No fishing for me today.

LOL...I'm up at 5:40 every morning for work....I had a PM so I checked that.  Good guess about steelhead fishing though...I'd likely be up at that time to do that as well.  I've been at the office since 715 this morning....
Good morning Tom... now go get the fishin' gear out and catch us a Wall-ice!
